data.title: FamilyTreeDNA
data.meta_description: Discover your DNA story and unlock the secrets of your ancestry and genealogy with our autosomal DNA, Y-DNA, and mtDNA tests.
data.text: Welcome to Kyiv Region DNA Geographical Project! All people who trace their ancestry to Kyivan region, including it's maximum extent in the times of the medieval Principality of Kyiv, Kyiv Voivodeship and Kyiv Governorate. The aim of the project is to study the Kyiv region's Y-DNA, mtDNA and auDNA composition as well as to be a hub for all the people whose ancestors are from the region and hope to find more information. Kyiv is the oldest Eastern European and Slavic city with unique and rich history. It was the major trade hub and a political hub through middle ages. The project might shed light on patterns of migration and settlement of various tribes throughout the region and beyond.
